                   в”Ӯ в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ в”Ӯ\r\nв”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө\r\nв”Ӯ Resumo                        в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ Produtos        R$ 499,70     в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ Frete           R$ 0,00       в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ Total           R$ 499,70     в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ                               в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ [Finalizar compra]            в”Ӯ\r\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\r\n```\r\n\r\nClasses principais:\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<section class=\"bg-shop-background px-4 py-5\">\r\n  <h1 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-shop-text\">Meu carrinho</h1>\r\n\r\n  <div class=\"mt-4 space-y-3\">\r\n    <article class=\"rounded-2xl border border-shop-border bg-shop-surface p-4\">\r\n      <h2 class=\"font-medium text-shop-text\">Fone Bluetooth</h2>\r\n      <p class=\"mt-1 font-bold text-shop-price\">R$ 199,90</p>\r\n\r\n      <button class=\"mt-2 text-sm font-medium text-shop-danger\">\r\n        Remover\r\n      </button>\r\n    </article>\r\n  </div>\r\n\r\n  <aside class=\"mt-5 rounded-2xl bg-shop-surface p-4 shadow-sm\">\r\n    <h2 class=\"font-semibold text-shop-text\">Resumo</h2>\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-shop-text-muted\">\r\n      <div class=\"flex justify-between\">\r\n        <span>Produtos</span>\r\n        <span>R$ 499,70</span>\r\n      </div>\r\n\r\n      <div class=\"flex justify-between\">\r\n        <span>Frete</span>\r\n        <span class=\"text-shop-free-shipping\">R$ 0,00</span>\r\n      </div>\r\n\r\n      <div class=\"flex justify-between border-t border-shop-border pt-3 text-lg font-bold text-shop-text\">\r\n        <span>Total</span>\r\n        <span>R$ 499,70</span>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n    <button class=\"mt-4 w-full rounded-xl bg-shop-primary px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-shop-text-inverted hover:bg-shop-primary-hover\">\r\n      Finalizar compra\r\n    </button>\r\n  </aside>\r\n</section>\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Desktop\r\n\r\n```text\r\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\r\nв”Ӯ Meu carrinho                                                 в”Ӯ\r\nв”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө\r\nв”Ӯ Produtos                                 в”Ӯ Resumo do pedido  в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ [Produto]                                в”Ӯ Produtos R$ 499   в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ [Produto]                                в”Ӯ Frete    R$ 0     в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ                                          в”Ӯ Total    R$ 499   в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ                                          в”Ӯ [Finalizar compra]в”Ӯ\r\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\r\n```\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## 10. PГЎgina ГҒrea do Cliente\r\n\r\n### Objetivo\r\n\r\nPermitir que o cliente altere seus dados, altere sua senha e consulte seus pedidos.\r\n\r\n### Mobile\r\n\r\n```text\r\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\r\nв”Ӯ вҶҗ Minha conta             рҹӣ’  в”Ӯ\r\nв”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө\r\nв”Ӯ OlГЎ, Cliente                  в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ cliente@email.com             в”Ӯ\r\nв”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө\r\nв”Ӯ [Meus dados]                  в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ [Alterar senha]               в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ [Meus pedidos]                в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ [EndereГ§os]                   в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ [Sair da conta]               в”Ӯ\r\nв”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө\r\nв”Ӯ Гҡltimos pedidos               в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ Pedido #1023                  в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ Status: Em transporte         в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ Total: R$ 399,90              в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ [Ver detalhes]                в”Ӯ\r\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\r\n```\r\n\r\nClasses principais:\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<section class=\"bg-shop-background px-4 py-5\">\r\n  <div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-shop-surface p-4 shadow-sm\">\r\n    <h1 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-shop-text\">Minha conta</h1>\r\n    <p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-shop-text-muted\">cliente@email.com</p>\r\n  </div>\r\n\r\n  <nav class=\"mt-4 space-y-2\">\r\n    <a class=\"block rounded-xl bg-shop-surface px-4 py-3 font-medium text-shop-text\" href=\"/account/profile\">\r\n      Meus dados\r\n    </a>\r\n\r\n    <a class=\"block rounded-xl bg-shop-surface px-4 py-3 font-medium text-shop-text\" href=\"/account/password\">\r\n      Alterar senha\r\n    </a>\r\n\r\n    <a class=\"block rounded-xl bg-shop-surface px-4 py-3 font-medium text-shop-text\" href=\"/account/orders\">\r\n      Meus pedidos\r\n    </a>\r\n\r\n    <button class=\"block w-full rounded-xl bg-shop-danger-soft px-4 py-3 text-left font-medium text-shop-danger\">\r\n      Sair da conta\r\n    </button>\r\n  </nav>\r\n</section>\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Desktop\r\n\r\n```text\r\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\r\nв”Ӯ Minha conta                                                  в”Ӯ\r\nв”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө\r\nв”Ӯ Menu lateral          в”Ӯ ConteГәdo                             в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ Meus dados            в”Ӯ Dados pessoais                       в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ Alterar senha         в”Ӯ Nome                                 в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ Meus pedidos          в”Ӯ E-mail                               в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ EndereГ§os             в”Ӯ Telefone                             в”Ӯ\r\nв”Ӯ Sair                  в”Ӯ [Salvar alteraГ§Гөes]                  в”Ӯ\r\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\r\n```\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## 11. NavegaГ§ГЈo recomendada\r\n\r\n### Mobile\r\n\r\n```text\r\nв”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ\r\nв”Ӯ  рҹҸ  Home   рҹ”Һ Busca   рҹ§ҫ Pedidos   рҹ‘Ө Conta в”Ӯ\r\nв””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\r\n```\r\n\r\nClasses sugeridas:\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<nav class=\"fixed bottom-0 left-0 right-0 border-t border-shop-border bg-shop-surface\">\r\n  <div class=\"grid grid-cols-4 text-center text-xs text-shop-text-muted\">\r\n    <a class=\"py-3 hover:text-shop-primary\" href=\"/\">Home</a>\r\n    <a class=\"py-3 hover:text-shop-primary\" href=\"/products\">Busca</a>\r\n    <a class=\"py-3 hover:text-shop-primary\" href=\"/account/orders\">Pedidos</a>\r\n    <a class=\"py-3 hover:text-shop-primary\" href=\"/account\">Conta</a>\r\n  </div>\r\n</nav>\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Desktop\r\n\r\n```text\r\nShop API | Busca | Ofertas | Categorias | Meus Pedidos | Carrinho | Conta\r\n```\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## 12. Rotas sugeridas\r\n\r\n| PГЎgina              | Rota                |\r\n| ------------------- | ------------------- |\r\n| Login               | `/login`            |\r\n| Home                | `/`                 |\r\n| CatГЎlogo            | `/products`         |\r\n| Detalhes do Produto | `/products/:id`     |\r\n| Carrinho            | `/cart`             |\r\n| ГҒrea do Cliente     | `/account`          |\r\n| Meus Dados          | `/account/profile`  |\r\n| Alterar Senha       | `/account/password` |\r\n| Meus Pedidos        | `/account/orders`   |\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## 13. Componentes reutilizГЎveis\r\n\r\n```text\r\n/components\r\n  /layout\r\n    Header\r\n    MobileBottomNavigation\r\n    Footer\r\n    PageContainer\r\n\r\n  /product\r\n    ProductCard\r\n    ProductGrid\r\n    ProductGallery\r\n    ProductPrice\r\n    ProductRating\r\n    ProductSpecifications\r\n\r\n  /cart\r\n    CartButton\r\n    CartItem\r\n    CartSummary\r\n    QuantitySelector\r\n\r\n  /customer\r\n    AccountMenu\r\n    ProfileForm\r\n    PasswordForm\r\n    OrdersList\r\n    OrderStatusBadge\r\n\r\n  /forms\r\n    Input\r\n    Checkbox\r\n    Button\r\n    Alert\r\n    FormError\r\n```\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## 14. Breakpoints recomendados\r\n\r\n| Breakpoint       | Uso                            |\r\n| ---------------- | ------------------------------ |\r\n| `0px - 480px`    | Mobile pequeno                 |\r\n| `481px - 768px`  | Mobile grande / tablet pequeno |\r\n| `769px - 1024px` | Tablet / desktop compacto      |\r\n| `1025px+`        | Desktop completo               |\r\n\r\n### Grid de produtos\r\n\r\n| Dispositivo    | Colunas |\r\n| -------------- | ------: |\r\n| Mobile pequeno |       2 |\r\n| Mobile grande  |       2 |\r\n| Tablet         |       3 |\r\n| Desktop        |       4 |\r\n| Desktop largo  |       5 |\r\n\r\nClasses sugeridas:\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 xl:grid-cols-5\">\r\n  <!-- produtos -->\r\n</div>\r\n```\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## 15. Estados importantes da interface\r\n\r\n### Produto indisponГӯvel\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<div class=\"rounded-xl bg-shop-warning-soft p-4 text-shop-warning\">\r\n  Produto sem estoque.\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<button class=\"mt-3 rounded-xl border border-shop-warning px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-shop-warning\">\r\n  Avise-me quando chegar\r\n</button>\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Carrinho vazio\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<section class=\"flex min-h-[60vh] flex-col items-center justify-center bg-shop-background px-4 text-center\">\r\n  <h1 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-shop-text\">Seu carrinho estГЎ vazio</h1>\r\n\r\n  <p class=\"mt-2 text-shop-text-muted\">\r\n    Explore nossas ofertas e encontre produtos incrГӯveis.\r\n  </p>\r\n\r\n  <a\r\n    href=\"/products\"\r\n    class=\"mt-5 rounded-xl bg-shop-primary px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-shop-text-inverted hover:bg-shop-primary-hover\"\r\n  >\r\n    Ver produtos\r\n  </a>\r\n</section>\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Cliente nГЈo logado\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-shop-surface p-5 text-center shadow-sm\">\r\n  <h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-shop-text\">Entre para acessar sua conta</h2>\r\n\r\n  <p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-shop-text-muted\">\r\n    VocГӘ precisa estar logado para consultar seus pedidos e alterar seus dados.\r\n  </p>\r\n\r\n  <a\r\n    href=\"/login\"\r\n    class=\"mt-5 inline-block rounded-xl bg-shop-primary px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-shop-text-inverted hover:bg-shop-primary-hover\"\r\n  >\r\n    Entrar\r\n  </a>\r\n</div>\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Erro no login\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<div class=\"rounded-xl bg-shop-danger-soft p-3 text-sm font-medium text-shop-danger\">\r\n  E-mail ou senha invГЎlidos. Verifique seus dados e tente novamente.\r\n</div>\r\n```\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n## 16. Resumo da proposta\r\n\r\nA Shop API deve utilizar uma UI mobile first com:\r\n\r\n* Tema suave baseado em Tailwind CSS 4;\r\n* Azul como cor principal de aГ§ГЈo;\r\n* Laranja para ofertas e chamadas promocionais;\r\n* Fundo claro e limpo;\r\n* Cards brancos com bordas suaves;\r\n* Busca em destaque;\r\n* Carrinho sempre no canto superior direito;\r\n* Home com ofertas, categorias e catГЎlogo;\r\n* PГЎgina de produto focada em imagem, preГ§o e compra;\r\n* Carrinho simples e objetivo;\r\n* ГҒrea do cliente organizada por dados, senha e pedidos.\r\n\r\nA proposta deixa a Shop API com aparГӘncia de loja virtual real, boa usabilidade e base visual consistente para implementaГ§ГЈo em React, Next.js, Vue, Angular ou qualquer stack frontend moderna.\r\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
